{"name": "matchescu-base", "metadata": {"name": "matchescu-base", "version": "0.7.0", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1732718520}, "documentation": ["# matchescu-base\nCommon abstract data types (`adt` package) and utilities\n(`common` package) for the **matchescu** entity resolution\ncomparison framework.\n\n## Set up dev environment\n\n1. (_optional_) install pyenv\n2. install Python 3.11\n3. install [Poetry](https://python-poetry.org)\n4. clone this repository\n5. run a couple of shell commands\n```shell\n$ cd <REPO_ROOT>\n$ poetry install\n```\n\n## Run tests\n\n```shell\n$ poetry run pytest\n```\n\n## Activate virtual environment\n\n```shell\n$ poetry shell\n```\n-or-\n```shell\n$ source .venv/bin/activate\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "matchescu.data", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "matchescu.data.EntityReferenceExtraction", "xref": {"fqname": "matchescu.data._extraction.EntityReferenceExtraction", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "matchescu.data._extraction", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "matchescu.data._extraction.EntityReferenceExtraction", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "matchescu.data._extraction.EntityReferenceExtraction.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "ds", "type": {"name": "DataSource", "xref": {"fqname": "matchescu.typing._data.DataSource", "project": null}, "params": [{"name": "T", "xref": {"fqname": "matchescu.typing._data.T", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "id_factory", "type": {"name": "EntityReferenceIdFactory", "xref": {"fqname": "matchescu.typing._entity_resolution.EntityRefe